**/dgph
*.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
*.moved-aside
*.pbxuser
*.perspectivev3
**/*sync/
.sconsign.dblite
.tags*
**/.vagrant/
**/DerivedData/
Icon?
**/Pods/
**/.symlinks/
profile
xcuserdata
**/.generated/
Flutter/App.framework
Flutter/Flutter.framework
